Date: 2014/10/01
Title: Epigenomic tools
Author: Mark Robinson <mark.robinson@imls.uzh.ch>, Dario Strbenac
        <d.strbenac@garvan.org.au>, Aaron Statham
        <a.statham@garvan.org.au>, Andrea Riebler
